  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Tutorial_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: e00198e87a257ff41b02cc989c3a409a, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items:
    - rid: 2319839819189715041
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 11264212992
    m_Localized: Hello! Welcome to Pantory!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 2319839819189715041
  - m_Id: 438890283008
    m_Localized: Pantory is a factory management simulation game.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 575934971904
    m_Localized: First, a quick overview of the UI. You can reopen this help anytime
      with the (?) button on each main panel.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1678642659328
    m_Localized: Credits and Research Points are shown at the top left; tap there
      for details.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2291514359808
    m_Localized: This container displays the employment status, allocation status,
      and satisfaction level of employees.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2320476028928
    m_Localized: This strip shows the in-game date and clock, plus buttons to reopen
      the tutorial or open settings.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2777508364288
    m_Localized: Use these icons to jump between Storage, Orders, Market, Staff, Research,
      News, and Finance. You can also press F1 through F9 for the same shortcuts.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5943566155776
    m_Localized: Logistics is the core of your factory. Build a line by connecting
      stations and production buildings with roads, then keep every input and output
      direction aligned so packets can continue moving without delay.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7203816095744
    m_Localized: Typical flow is Unload → roads → production buildings → roads →
      Load. Unload pulls raw materials in, factories process them, and Load sends
      finished goods toward storage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7579063697408
    m_Localized: Place buildings and roads from this panel. Select an item, preview
      rotation on the grid, and click to build. You can also hold placement input
      for continuous placement to quickly lay long road lines.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7894026567680
    m_Localized: Building buttons are grouped by category. Distribution includes
      roads, splitter, and tunnel. Use splitter to alternate one input into two outputs,
      and use tunnel to pass vertical and horizontal traffic independently without
      blocking each other.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8131256401920
    m_Localized: Track resource inventory in this panel. If a line stalls, first
      check whether upstream materials are available, then verify road direction,
      building orientation, and whether outputs are connected to valid destinations.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9056704413696
    m_Localized: Good logistics design means short paths, clear direction, and balanced
      outputs. Expand gradually, watch for bottlenecks, and use splitter/tunnel strategically
      to keep throughput stable as your factory grows.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11779361357824
    m_Localized: This switch toggles build/remove mode. In remove mode, deleting
      a building also clears its worker/technician assignments, so review staffing
      after major layout changes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12960301203456
    m_Localized: This is the storage panel. This panel shows you the inventory of
      resources you currently have.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 13340426780672
    m_Localized: Every resource belongs to a category; use the filters here to narrow
      the list.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17836750028800
    m_Localized: This is the Orders panel. Clients request materials; accept a contract,
      then deliver the listed resources before the deadline.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17928651423744
    m_Localized: Clients belong to three types—Government, Company, and Individual.
      Higher Wealth unlocks access to Government and Company jobs, and requested
      quantities scale with your Wealth as well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 18539786682368
    m_Localized: You can filter where each order came from here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 18834268766208
    m_Localized: Use this switch to move between new requests and contracts you have
      already accepted.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19061579071488
    m_Localized: A list of clients by client category can be found here. Clicking
      on a client will display a list of orders available to that client.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19397370855424
    m_Localized: New orders appear here. Click to accept an order and it will move
      to your accepted orders list.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19716532224000
    m_Localized: This is the Market panel. Here you can buy and sell resources and
      view information about competing companies.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 22018345287680
    m_Localized: Here you can choose whether to display the resource view or the
      trader (competitor) view via the button.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 22020337582080
    m_Localized: This is the Resource View. You can adjust your current resource
      purchase and sale volume here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24215317528576
    m_Localized: Resource information is displayed here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24483870425088
    m_Localized: The price history of resources is visually displayed here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24698149027840
    m_Localized: This is the Trader (Competitor) View. You can view information about
      each trader.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 36510642880512
    m_Localized: This is the panel where you can manage your employees.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 36904429305856
    m_Localized: This shows your current management capacity. A certain number of
      managers are required per employee. If you are short on managers, employee
      satisfaction will be penalized.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 37440536854528
    m_Localized: Employee satisfaction is affected by many factors. You can see what
      is affecting it here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 37828904239104
    m_Localized: Employee efficiency depends on satisfaction, and that efficiency
      directly affects building work speed and production throughput.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 38302378246144
    m_Localized: The easiest way to raise employee satisfaction is to pay them more.
      Lower pay will reduce it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39086448852992
    m_Localized: Employees are divided into Workers, Technicians, Researchers, and
      Managers. Workers and Technicians are assigned to buildings, Researchers produce
      RP, and Managers support organization-wide management.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39688935456768
    m_Localized: Here, you can decide whether to hire or fire employees. Hiring or
      firing employees costs credits, and firing employees will decrease their satisfaction.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2561770013474816
    m_Localized: This is the research panel. You can unlock buildings and boost productivity.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2562082698838016
    m_Localized: This is where you can see your Research Points (RP) and how many
      Research Points you gain each day.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2562316594200576
    m_Localized: This is a panel where you can see the number of researchers and
      the effects they are receiving.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2562738453102592
    m_Localized: This is the research tree. Finished nodes are tinted, and the next
      linked projects unlock once their prerequisites are met.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2563160425250816
    m_Localized: This is the Finance panel, where you can view your company's growth
      over time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2564533472608256
    m_Localized: Shows your current monthly growth rate.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2565297930649600
    m_Localized: Shows your current monthly profit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2566859943985152
    m_Localized: Shows your current company value in a graph.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2566981499109376
    m_Localized: Shows your current credits in a graph.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
